SFORM]].*  '''FUNC_LESS_THAN''' = '''4'''  Comparison for less than ({{Span|a < b}}). Cannot be used if [[#type|type]] set to [[VisualShaderNodeCompare GD#CTYPE_BOOLEAN|CTYPE_BOOLEAN]] or [[VisualShaderNodeCompare GD#CTYPE_TRANSFORM|CTYPE_TRANSFORM]].*  '''FUNC_LESS_THAN_EQUAL''' = '''5'''  Comparison for less than or equal ({{Span|a <= b}}). Cannot be used if [[#type|type]] set to [[VisualShaderNodeCompare GD#CTYPE_BOOLEAN|CTYPE_BOOLEAN]] or [[VisualShaderNodeCompare GD#CTYPE_TRANSFORM|CTYPE_TRANSFORM]].=== Condition ====== COND_ALL ====== COND_ANY ===enum '''Condition''':*  '''COND_ALL''' = '''0'''  The result will be true if all of component in vector satisfy the comparison condition.*  '''COND_ANY''' = '''1'''  The result will be true if any of component in vector satisfy the comparison condition.== Property Descriptions ===== condition ===*  [[#Condition|Condition]] '''condition'''{| class="wikitable | ''Default''|| {{Span|0}}                |-| ''Setter''|| set_condition(value) |-| ''Getter''|| get_condition()      |}Extra condition which is applied if [[#type|type]] is set to [[VisualShaderNodeCompare GD#CTYPE_VECTOR|CTYPE_VECTOR]].=== function ===*  [[#Function|Function]] '''function'''{| class="wikitable | ''Default''|| {{Span|0}}               |-| ''Setter''|| set_function(value) |-| ''Getter''|| get_function()      |}A comparison function. See [[#Function|Function]] for options.=== type ===*  [[#ComparisonType|ComparisonType]] '''type'''{| class="wikitable | ''Default''|| {{Span|0}}                      |-| ''Setter''|| set_comparison_type(value) |-| ''Getter''|| get_comparison_type()      |}The type to be used in the comparison. See [[#ComparisonType|ComparisonType]] for options.